[
  {
    "startTime": 4.25,
    "endTime": 7.37,
    "text": "- Reyka says I'm crazy, but if I was being Truman Show'd,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.37,
    "endTime": 9.31,
    "text": "you'd tell me, right Siobhan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.31,
    "endTime": 13.440000000000001,
    "text": "- What? Raph, you're crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.44,
    "endTime": 14.709,
    "text": "- [Male Voice] Change the subject."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.71,
    "endTime": 17.07,
    "text": "- I'm going to get a drink, you guys want anything?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.07,
    "endTime": 18.32,
    "text": "Siobhan, Ralph?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.32,
    "endTime": 20.029,
    "text": "- [Siobhan] I'm perfectly fine, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.029,
    "endTime": 21.26,
    "text": "- No, no thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.26,
    "endTime": 22.093,
    "text": "- All righty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.095,
    "endTime": 26.229,
    "text": "- Hey, Siobhan, I notice that your friend"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.23,
    "endTime": 27.25,
    "text": "keeps calling me Ralph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.25,
    "endTime": 28.71,
    "text": "- Oh, really? I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.71,
    "endTime": 30.25,
    "text": "- Do you think you could correct her for me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.25,
    "endTime": 31.9,
    "text": "- Ooh, why can't you do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.9,
    "endTime": 33.559,
    "text": "- Well, I don't want to be rude, she's your friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.56,
    "endTime": 35.74,
    "text": "- Well, I don't wanna be rude, she's my friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.74,
    "endTime": 38.45,
    "text": "- Alright, maybe I can do it naturally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.45,
    "endTime": 39.283,
    "text": "- Back, dummies!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.47,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "- Ralph, aren't you warm?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 43.47,
    "text": "Don't you want to take off your jacket?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.47,
    "endTime": 45.589,
    "text": "- You know what, Raph's pretty comfortable actually,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.59,
    "endTime": 47.24,
    "text": "but that's classic Raph, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.24,
    "endTime": 48.291000000000004,
    "text": "- Classic Raph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.291,
    "endTime": 50.247,
    "text": "- It's like my mom always used to tell me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.247,
    "endTime": 51.9,
    "text": "\"Raph, your name is Raph,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.9,
    "endTime": 53.53,
    "text": "just in case there's any confusion, Raph.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.53,
    "endTime": 55.550000000000004,
    "text": "- Jeez, sounds like your mom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.55,
    "endTime": 57.23,
    "text": "thinks you're pretty dumb, Ralph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.23,
    "endTime": 59.22,
    "text": "- Did your mom name you after the painter?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.22,
    "endTime": 61.121,
    "text": "- Yes, yes, that's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.121,
    "endTime": 63.330000000000005,
    "text": "- Ralphael the painter? Cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.33,
    "endTime": 66.01,
    "text": "- Nah, I think you added an extra L in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.01,
    "endTime": 68.433,
    "text": "- Oh, what, so it's Ralphae?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.33,
    "endTime": 70.46,
    "text": "- You know, most people think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.46,
    "endTime": 72.231,
    "text": "I was named after the ninja turtle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.231,
    "endTime": 73.372,
    "text": "- Donatello."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.372,
    "endTime": 74.95,
    "text": "- Donat- - I see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.95,
    "endTime": 78.78,
    "text": "- I am not Donatello! Unbelievable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.78,
    "endTime": 80.98,
    "text": "- Um, sorry, dude, are you drawing me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.98,
    "endTime": 83.13000000000001,
    "text": "Because I'm actually really protective over my image."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.13,
    "endTime": 85.679,
    "text": "- No, just doodling, (chuckles)."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.68,
    "endTime": 88.46000000000001,
    "text": "You guys ever spend the day just writing down your own name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.46,
    "endTime": 89.833,
    "text": "- No, never."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.9,
    "endTime": 91.733,
    "text": "Which is kinda weird,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.733,
    "endTime": 94.21000000000001,
    "text": "'cause I'm kind of a freak for word games."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.21,
    "endTime": 96.869,
    "text": "- Oh, right, yeah, Angela, ooh, here's a good one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.87,
    "endTime": 101.13300000000001,
    "text": "What is a four letter word that is short for Raphael?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.408,
    "endTime": 103.241,
    "text": "- Ooh, Ralph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.241,
    "endTime": 105.51,
    "text": "- What? That's five letters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.51,
    "endTime": 108.5,
    "text": "We're looking for one, two, three, four."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.5,
    "endTime": 109.533,
    "text": "- Dude, look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.205,
    "endTime": 114.366,
    "text": "Ra-lf"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.366,
    "endTime": 117.66,
    "text": "Ralf, it's your name, dummy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.66,
    "endTime": 118.512,
    "text": "- No it's not!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.36,
    "text": "Don't you think it's weird"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.36,
    "endTime": 123.043,
    "text": "that you're the only one who calls me that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.043,
    "endTime": 125.683,
    "text": "- Am I the only person that calls you Ralph?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.64,
    "endTime": 127.88,
    "text": "I feel so honored."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.88,
    "endTime": 129.359,
    "text": "- That is actually really sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.36,
    "endTime": 130.276,
    "text": "- Not it's not, it's not-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.276,
    "endTime": 132.42000000000002,
    "text": "- Raph - Ralph"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.42,
    "endTime": 133.253,
    "text": "- Raph - Rafff"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.253,
    "endTime": 134.32299999999998,
    "text": "- Ralph! - Raph!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.324,
    "endTime": 135.591,
    "text": "- Ralph! - Rruff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.591,
    "endTime": 136.709,
    "text": "- Raph! - Ralph!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.709,
    "endTime": 137.643,
    "text": "- Ruff, ruff, ruff. - Ralph, Ralph, Ralph, Ralph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.643,
    "endTime": 138.71,
    "text": "- It's Raph!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.71,
    "endTime": 140.47,
    "text": "- Who are you talking to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.47,
    "endTime": 142.04,
    "text": "- Who are you talking to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.04,
    "endTime": 146.286,
    "text": "My name is not Ralph, it's Raph-i-el, or Ra-pha-el,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.286,
    "endTime": 149.613,
    "text": "or Ra-phi-el, or Ra-pha-el, or Raf, or Raph, or Raif."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.17,
    "endTime": 152.003,
    "text": "I don't get bummed by Raif!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.003,
    "endTime": 156.66,
    "text": "Or Raphi, or Rapha, or Raphi, any of those would work,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.66,
    "endTime": 159.82,
    "text": "just not Ralph."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.82,
    "endTime": 160.959,
    "text": "- It's a nickname."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.96,
    "endTime": 163.084,
    "text": "- It's not, though!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.084,
    "endTime": 166.05,
    "text": "It's a totally different name unto itself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.05,
    "endTime": 167.46,
    "text": "- But it's a diminutive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.46,
    "endTime": 169.1,
    "text": "- What would it be short for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.1,
    "endTime": 172.59,
    "text": "It's a short name, but it isn't short for anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.59,
    "endTime": 173.75,
    "text": "- Don't people call you Af?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.75,
    "endTime": 175.05,
    "text": "- Oh, Reyka does call you Af."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.05,
    "endTime": 176.5,
    "text": "- We are still in litigation!"
  }
]